    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>Brilliant sunlight flashes in a 60-foot radius centered on a point you choose within range. Each creature in that light must make a &amp;Reference[con]{Constitution} saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 12d6 &amp;Reference[radiant]{radiant} damage and is &amp;Reference[blinded]{blinded} for 1 minute. On a successful save, it takes half as much damage and isn't &amp;Reference[blinded]{blinded} by this spell. &amp;Reference[undead]{Undead} and oozes have disadvantage on this saving throw.</p>\n<p>A creature &amp;Reference[blinded]{blinded} by this spell makes another &amp;Reference[con]{Constitution} saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a successful save, it is no longer &amp;Reference[blinded]{blinded}.</p>\n<p>This spell dispels any darkness in its area that was created by a spell.</p>\n</div>",
